    </div>
    <div class="footer-section">
      <h3>Connect</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://aiddbot.com" target="_blank"><b>AIDDbot </b></a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/AlbertoBasalo" target="_blank">GitHub</a></li>
